### **3️⃣ The Personal Computing Revolution (1970s-1990s)**

- **Microprocessors (1971)** – Intel 4004 revolutionized computing.
- **Apple, IBM PCs (1976-1981)** – Home computing becomes mainstream.
- **The Internet (1980s-1990s)** – Birth of the World Wide Web (Tim Berners-Lee, 1989).

