## 🏆 **Pioneers & Innovators**

|**Name**|**Contribution**|
|---|---|
|**Ada Lovelace**|First programmer, designed algorithms for Babbage’s engine.|
|**Alan Turing**|Theoretical model for modern computing, WWII codebreaking.|
|**Grace Hopper**|Invented COBOL, developed first compiler.|
|**John von Neumann**|Architect of stored-program computers.|
|**Tim Berners-Lee**|Invented the World Wide Web.|
|**Gladys West**|Developed GPS mathematics.|
|**Philip Emeagwali**|Early contributions to supercomputing.|

